{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/181/comments/92891489.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/diff/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo:a030012020a7..650f5e3ca384?path=src%2Fsystems%2Flog%2FLogRecord.cc"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/181/_/diff#comment-92891489"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 181, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pullrequests/181.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gazebo/pull-requests/181"}}, "title": "[Acropolis] Add logging"}, "content": {"raw": "How about having a default path where logs are saved to in case the path is not set by the user? On Gazebo 9, logs end up under `~/.gazebo/log/<timestamp>` by default. We could use `~/.ignition/gazebo/log/<timestamp>` here.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>How about having a default path where logs are saved to in case the path is not set by the user? On Gazebo 9, logs end up under <code>~/.gazebo/log/&lt;timestamp&gt;</code> by default. We could use <code>~/.ignition/gazebo/log/&lt;timestamp&gt;</code> here.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-02-26T01:45:40.468392+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "inline": {"to": 67, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "src/systems/log/LogRecord.cc"}, "updated_on": "2019-02-26T01:45:57.27840